description:
The Jester has yet to see a win. She got her ass handed to her by The Goddess, and Tony, however she only lost by 35pts to The Trouper. She as 3 matches of experience. And desperately wants a win.
The Deceptacon came into US and won her first match! She beat The Brawler who had 3 matches under her belt. She is strong, has endurance as has experience. She wants to start her career (2-0) undefeated. Instead she got a brutal ass fucking.
title: The Deceptacon (1-0) The Jester (0-3)
